### No Visible Label Use Aria Label For Accessibility

```tsx
() => (
  <div>
    <h3>No Visible Label Example</h3>
    <Dropdown
      data-automation-id="arialabelexample"
      aria-label="Choose a fruit"
      className={styles.exampleDropdown}
      onChange={action('onChange')}
    >
      <MenuItem value="1">Banana</MenuItem>
      <MenuItem value="2">Apple</MenuItem>
      <MenuItem value="3">Guava</MenuItem>
      <MenuItem value="4">Mango</MenuItem>
      <MenuItem value="5">Orange</MenuItem>
      <MenuItem value="6">Pear</MenuItem>
      <MenuItem value="7">Strawberry</MenuItem>
      <MenuItem value="8">Watermelon</MenuItem>
      <MenuItem value="9">Blueberry</MenuItem>
      <MenuItem value="10">Pineapple</MenuItem>
    </Dropdown>
    <p>
      The element is used to associate a text label with a form field. The label
